<p>Ward bulletin inserts can be an effective way of generating interest in the  program. Inserts are designed to quickly display a small amount of information about the program, targeting a ward audience. Effective ways  to use inserts include:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Ward bulletin</strong>: Ask your local priesthood to put inserts in the bulletin board.&nbsp;Each sheet has three different inserts; print all three. Then put a different insert in each program. The variety adds interest.</li>
</ul>
<h3>How to get them</h3>
<p>Download the correct version by clicking on the document that is for your area. These files can be customized to include your own contact information. Where possible, color copies are recommended.</p>
